{"tid":1534597,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲野想話俾覺得依家個運動太暴力嘅你知","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T10:17:12.000Z","uid":138834,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2d15b78d3a8d9c4b5762ca5c9faa194c37c51f7c","tid":1534597,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:08:10.000Z","msg":"首先，我只係個低學歷地盤佬，英文唔識多隻<br />\n講唔出咩大道理，但有啲野同你哋講<br />\n<br />\n法律由暴力支撐,冇暴力的法律形同虛設<br />\n所以首先希望你唔好對暴力咁反感<br />\n<br />\n然後我哋都知道一般而言我哋會將司法機構,立法機構,政府等所持有嘅暴力稱為武力<br />\n因為我們相信,該機構行使嘅暴力是受監管嘅力量,是在法治之下所行使<br />\n<br />\n但法治並非就如字面所指單單去依法而治<br />\n並唔係話所有人都受同一法律制裁就係法治<br />\n<br />\n任何法律嘅成立/執行,特權,以至所有公權力嘅行使都有一個前提<br />\n<br />\n就係認受性,亦即&ldquo;被統治者的同意&rdquo;<br />\n現代社會而言,依份認受性一般係透過公開,公平,公正的選舉表達<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢講現今嘅政府沒有認受性,因為市民就連表達認受與否嘅權利都冇<br />\n依家街上的年青人都正為自己為我哋去爭取依項權利<br />\n<br />\n而佢哋嘅行動已經得到認受性,至少已得到我同意<br />\n<br />\n想深入了解下的話，我推薦幾本書俾你哋<br />\n<br />\n暴力的批判<br />\n暴力與社會秩序：詮釋有文字記載的人類歷史的一個概念性框架<br />\n<br />\nsorry因為我英文差，又搵唔到正體中文<br />\n只可以睇簡體同日文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4967381bd57b728cb065fb6bfb4d225a158ae846","tid":1534597,"uid":143699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:08:21.000Z","msg":"大家真係冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n-最近黨鐵多咗狗，如果情況唔允許，希望大家都唔好勉強，可以改用老人卡。唔好因為咁而被人捉。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFKdOOFpqpiAZGwRsEzlRJXk%3D&h=a204eb19\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"d962a6e1b243099d1581b90781923b8e05859258","tid":1534597,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df584ae30fc4b7c8d72fa6d89cfb3aec6dddbc37","tid":1534597,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:17:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金 全民提款日</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"4c0cc96bb4e903424107434e192c609cb730c4a9","tid":1534597,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:42:18.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"a32b21508941d9a8d1f22efbc6b2e8b548380963","tid":1534597,"uid":138834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}